
teacher_translation_engine.core
Author: Jose Luis Antonio Calderón
System Name: Teacher Translation Engine

Purpose:
To preserve, encode, and transmit the unique systems of real teachers across disciplines—
ensuring legacy and instructional truth beyond the lifespan of the teacher.

This engine:
- Accepts input only from verified human masters
- Uses the Calderón Method to break down their system into:
  * Core principles
  * Sealed teaching modules
  * Instructional tone + sequence
- Protects their authorship and moral code
- Ensures no outside modification or commercialization

Sealed by the author.
